# HSM collector conformance v1 — pre-aggregated partial bar (AddPartial) contract.
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|...
# Actions:
# add_int_bar_partial|bar_index|min|max|mean|first|last|count
# add_double_bar_partial|bar_index|min|max|mean|first|last|count
# Contract notes:
# - Partials merge by min/max union, weighted mean (sum += mean*count), first-of-first, last-of-last.
# - Int partials are validated strictly: count >= 1 and mean/first/last inside [min, max] inclusive.
# - Double partials tolerate FP drift: tolerance = max(1e-12, |max-min| * 1e-9).
# - An invalid partial is silently skipped — the call succeeds and the bar stays unchanged.

int_partial_single_passthrough|create_collector
int_partial_single_passthrough|create_int_bar_sensor|contract/partial/single|3600000|0
int_partial_single_passthrough|start
int_partial_single_passthrough|add_int_bar_partial|0|1|5|3|1|5|4
int_partial_single_passthrough|stop
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_sent_count|1
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|min|1
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|max|5
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|mean|3
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|first|1
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|last|5
int_partial_single_passthrough|expect_bar_field|0|count|4

